data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION!! LOCATION!!! This charming property features three bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a basement with an outside entrance making it an ideal family home. The detached garage in the backyard provides ample space for storage, and the backyard is perfect for outdoor activities or simply relaxing with family and friends. Inside, the home is cozy and inviting, with plenty of natural light streaming in through the windows. The spacious living room provides a welcoming atmosphere, with a formal dining room. The kitchen is well-appointed with access to the backyard. Upstairs, the bedrooms are comfortable and spacious, with ample closet space. New Front Entryway pavers, Newer Gas Heating System (5 years). Private Driveway.  1 Minute away from Hillside Ave; Major Highways: Grand Central PKWY and Clearview EXPY and Queens Village Train Station, Close to Buses, Shopping Centers, Schools, and Restaurants, Low Taxes!! Make it your own before it's gone!!!
